sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Order UI
    participant S as Order Service
    participant API as API Controller
    participant Hub as SignalR Hub
    participant DB as Database

    U->>UI: Select Category -> Product
    UI->>UI: Add to Temporary Cart
    U->>UI: Convert "Ghi chú" (e.g., Ít đá)
    U->>UI: Click "Gửi Bếp" (Submit)
    
    UI->>S: CreateOrderAsync(TableId, Items)
    S->>API: POST /api/Orders
    
    API->>DB: Insert Order
    API->>DB: Insert OrderItems
    API->>DB: Update Table.Status = Occupied
    DB-->>API: Success
    
    par Real-time Notify
        API->>Hub: Send "OrderCreated"
        Hub-->>UI: Notify All Clients
        Hub-->>Kitchen: Notify Kitchen Screen
    end
    
    API-->>S: Return Created Order
    S-->>UI: Show Success Message
    UI->>UI: Clear Cart & Show Order Details
